{"type":null,"faqId":19326,"title":"忘记屏幕解锁密码或图案","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s3{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;color:blue;}\n.s4{font-family:Frutiger Next Com;font-weight:bold;}\n.s5{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>您可以通过升级手机的方法解决。升级后，手机内部存储中的数据将被删除。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>通过 </span><span class=\"s1\">microSD</span><span> 卡升级：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>进入 </span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s3\">http:</span><a name=\"_Hlt405039244\"><a name=\"_Hlt405039245\"><span class=\"s3\">/</span></a></a><span class=\"s3\">/consumer.huawei.com/cn</span></a><span> ，根据手机型号下载软件升级包。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>将升级包中的 </span><span class=\"s1\">dload</span><span> 文件夹放入 </span><span class=\"s1\">microSD</span><span> 卡根目录下。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span>手机在关机状态下，插入 </span><span class=\"s1\">microSD</span><span> 卡，同时按住电源键和音量上键，直到出现 </span><span class=\"s4\">Select Boot Mode</span><span> 界面，按音量上键选择</span><span class=\"s5\"> </span><span class=\"s4\">[Recovery Mode]</span><span>，按音量下键确认选择，再选择 </span><span class=\"s4\">apply update from external sdcard</span><span>，按电源键确认选择，手机进入升级模式开始升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>升级完成后手机将会恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s5\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若无法升级，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2467","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422608222000,"seriesProductName":"G628-TL00","visitedTimes":542,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"2","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}